### Get all categories
GET http://localhost:3000/api/categories HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Create new category
POST http://localhost:3000/api/categories HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": ""
}

### Update category
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/categories/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Computers"
}

### Get Category By Id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/categories/100 HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Delete Category
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/categories/3 HTTP/1.1